00:18:41.587 --> 00:18:43.055 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:21%
No self.

00:18:43.055 --> 00:18:44.290 align:middle line:85% position:48% size:28%
No duality.

00:18:44.991 --> 00:18:50.496 align:middle line:79% position:40% size:75%
Yet, there is still the 
"I am," the Anatta or no self.

00:18:53.733 --> 00:18:57.269 align:middle line:79% position:40% size:63%
In that emptiness is the
dawn of prajna or wisdom.

00:18:59.672 --> 00:19:01.807 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:56%
The understanding
that the imminent self

00:19:01.807 --> 00:19:04.877 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:43%
is far beyond the
play of duality,

00:19:04.877 --> 00:19:06.579 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:70%
beyond the entire continuum.

00:19:11.050 --> 00:19:16.756 align:middle line:79% position:40% size:75%
The imminent self is timeless,
unchanging, always now.

00:19:17.923 --> 00:19:21.894 align:middle line:79% position:42% size:70%
Enlightenment is the merging
of the primordial spiral,

00:19:21.894 --> 00:19:24.864 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:43%
the ever changing
manifested world,

00:19:24.864 --> 00:19:30.236 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:78%
or lotus, in which time unfolds
with your timeless being.

00:19:34.473 --> 00:19:38.277 align:middle line:79% position:42% size:70%
Your inner wiring grows like
an ever unfolding flower

00:19:38.277 --> 00:19:41.080 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:48%
as you disidentify 
with the self,

00:19:41.080 --> 00:19:43.382 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:61%
becoming a living bridge

00:19:43.382 --> 00:19:46.652 align:middle line:79% position:40% size:63%
between the world 
of time and the timeless.

00:20:09.575 --> 00:20:11.644 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:43%
Merely realizing
the imminent self

00:20:11.644 --> 00:20:13.813 align:middle line:79% position:42% size:53%
is only the beginning
of one's path.

00:20:14.613 --> 00:20:17.316 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:56%
Most people will have
to experience and lose

00:20:17.316 --> 00:20:20.519 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:61%
Samadhi countless times 
in meditation

00:20:20.519 --> 00:20:22.321 align:middle line:79% position:45% size:50%
before they are
able to integrate it

00:20:22.321 --> 00:20:24.023 align:middle line:85% position:50% size:65%
into other facets of life.

00:20:26.325 --> 00:20:29.495 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:56%
It's not unusual to
have profound insights

00:20:29.495 --> 00:20:32.665 align:middle line:79% position:41% size:58%
into the nature of your
being during meditation

00:20:32.665 --> 00:20:37.002 align:middle line:79% position:36% size:73%
or self-inquiry, only to find
yourself once again

00:20:37.002 --> 00:20:39.805 align:middle line:79% position:45% size:45%
falling back 
into old patterns.

00:20:39.805 --> 00:20:41.907 align:middle line:79% position:45% size:50%
Forgetting the truth
of who you are.

