be directed by the soul.

00:29:30.268 --> 00:29:33.538 align:middle line:79% position:40% size:63%
You can only become aware
of the soul's purpose

00:29:33.538 --> 00:29:36.208 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:65%
when you are able to
watch the conditioned self

00:29:36.208 --> 00:29:40.746 align:middle line:79% position:38% size:68%
and its endless pursuits...
and let them go.

