00:30:24.856 --> 00:30:29.094 align:middle line:79% position:36% size:73%
The French existentialist and
Nobel Prize winning author,

00:30:29.094 --> 00:30:32.898 align:middle line:79% position:44% size:61%
Albert Camus, solved the
situation of Sisyphus

00:30:32.898 --> 00:30:34.866 align:middle line:85% position:46% size:68%
as a metaphor for humanity.

00:30:35.634 --> 00:30:37.969 align:middle line:79% position:45% size:50%
