a complete and utter failure

00:31:47.038 --> 00:31:50.909 align:middle line:79% position:42% size:70%
of the egoic self to awaken
through its futile pursuits.

00:32:15.333 --> 00:32:20.205 align:middle line:79% position:43% size:65%
